{"tid":2338591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨軍：部署足夠黨奴防止平安夜有非法集結或被禁的社交群組聚集","createTime":"2020-12-24T06:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T06:36:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fde29d97fad44170d7c652aa300031a3e49efc95","tid":2338591,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:17:39.000Z","msg":"警方指會部署足夠警力防止平安夜有非法集結<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，留意到有人於網上號召其他人，今日在全港各區進行未經批准的集結，警方會在相關地點部署足夠警力，迅速果斷執法，強調絕不容忍任何違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n警方在社交網站表示，有關活動沒有獲得警方的不反對通知書，亦有可能違反限聚令，強調疫情仍然嚴峻，呼籲市民應做好防疫措施，盡量減少社交活動及避免到人多聚集的地方，亦不要參與任何未經批准集結或受禁的群組聚集。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2372073&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76Mc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=ac467efc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372073</a>"},{"pid":"d602323153ed448d9ebd791eb124456b5c0e72e1","tid":2338591,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:18:40.000Z","msg":"食屎啦黑狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903bf334fbec640d11d5edb51691a9da7620fa1c","tid":2338591,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"垃圾賤種淨係識得玩政治<br />\n有做嘢就唔會有咁多群組出現"},{"pid":"5f56c6934b4b0beb1ca9dbd3d310c384888fa115","tid":2338591,"uid":306914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:23:25.000Z","msg":"太好啦，黑警咁多單武漢肺炎感染，依家仲要大規模集結，三萬thx 又近咗一大步<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{